---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout
  title="About Kim — Kimberly Dumaine"
  description="Learn about Kimberly Dumaine's 30+ year journey as a psychic medium, trance channel, and spiritual counselor in Scottsdale, Arizona."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-kicker center">Her Story</span>
      <h1>About <em>Kim</em></h1>
      <p>A lifetime devoted to bridging the seen and unseen worlds.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="page-content">
      <div class="container prose">
        <p>
          Kimberly Dumaine, a highly gifted and respected intuitive, psychic medium,
          spiritual counselor, and metaphysical teacher, has been sharing her insights
          and messages from spirit with clients for over 30 years. Kim offers a variety
          of private and group sessions, spiritual development classes/workshops, public
          speaking engagements and spiritual counseling to clients nationally and abroad.
          She is also well known for her unique abilities as a Trance Medium, allowing the
          spirit of Dr. James Martin Peebles (1822&ndash;1922), a holistic physician and
          19th-century leader in the Spiritualist movement, to speak directly through her
          in a deep trance state.
        </p>
        <p>
          Kim is in private practice in Scottsdale, Arizona, her home since 1965, where
          she lives with her husband and daughter. She has devoted her life and her work
          to the study and practice of spiritual truths, training extensively in the areas
          of interpersonal communication, spirit communication, mediumship (both conscious
          and trance), hypnotherapy, energy healing, Reiki, spiritual counseling, animal
          communication, and metaphysical philosophy.
        </p>
        <p>
          With her advanced abilities as a medium and a clairvoyant, she has helped many
          reach a higher level of understanding and awareness of the multi-dimensional
          world that we all share. She believes and clearly demonstrates that spirit
          communication is not only possible but ultimately necessary in our quest for
          expanded consciousness and the evolvement of the human race. It is her goal to
          help people understand that everyone and everything is interconnected, constantly
          influencing each other&rsquo;s energy system, and to teach us how we can
          consciously affect each other in a positive way.
        </p>
        <p>
          Born in upstate New York, Kim was aware at an early age that she was different.
          Visions, spirit communications, out-of-body and astral-travel were part of her
          early experience. She often displayed a wisdom that was beyond her years, sensing
          energy, possessing an unexplained knowledge of events and people, and seeing and
          hearing spirits around her.
        </p>
        <p>
          At 17, Kim attended Arizona State University and earned a Bachelor of Science
          degree in Communication. During this time, a growing desire to learn more of her
          abilities led her to the teachings of psychology, philosophy, world religions,
          metaphysics, and spiritualism. As her understanding grew, so did her abilities.
          She discovered that she could sense and communicate not only with disincarnate
          spirits but also with other life forms &mdash; the animal kingdom, the plant
          kingdom, the deva spirits, off-planet energies, even the cells of the human body
          &mdash; all proved to have varying degrees of consciousness and the ability to
          communicate thoughts, feelings, energy and information to an open receiver such
          as herself.
        </p>
        <p>
          After college, Kim was guided to many teachers of metaphysical understanding to
          aid her on her path. She studied with two excellent trance mediums: Bob Copeland,
          who channeled &ldquo;Ashlam,&rdquo; a wise master who spoke through him, and Rev.
          William Rainen, a well-known trance medium and spiritual teacher who worked with
          Dr. James Peebles, a witty and wonderful spirit who shared a great deal of
          knowledge over many years with Kim. Through her experiences with these teachers
          and many others, Kim grew rapidly in her awareness of energy, past lives, the
          spirit world, and ultimately the path she was to take herself in this life as a
          channel and teacher.
        </p>
        <p>
          Kim knew that her mission in this lifetime was to share her perceptions and to
          assist others on their spiritual journeys with her unique abilities. Her goal
          with each and every person she speaks with is clear: to give hope and
          inspiration, to comfort those in sorrow, to help identify patterns of behavior
          or blocks that stopped or slowed their spiritual progress, to show them the many
          options that were theirs to choose, and to help them rediscover, understand and
          better utilize their personal power.
        </p>
        <p>
          As a result, Kim became trained in many complementary fields to further assist
          her clients &mdash; Trance Medium, Reiki Master, Therapeutic Touch, Auric Field
          Cleansing/energy healing, Hypnotherapy, Meditation Instruction, the use of
          visualization and imagery, and the power of affirmations. All have proven to be
          valuable tools in creating lasting change for many clients.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, Kim provides a variety of intuitive services and consultations, both
          in-person, by phone and online, to meet the diverse needs of her clients, locally
          and nationwide. She also offers metaphysical lectures, classes, trance
          demonstrations and workshops to teach people how to connect with their spiritual
          powers.
        </p>
        <div class="page-cta">
          <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}consultations/`} class="btn btn-glow">See Consultations &amp; Offerings</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
